# Trinity backend — Postgres connection.
# When set, imports and events are stored in the database and shared across the
# whole team. When unset, the app falls back to per-browser localStorage.
#
# Vercel injects one of these automatically when you connect a Postgres database
# to the project (Storage tab). POSTGRES_URL is preferred; DATABASE_URL also works.
POSTGRES_URL=
# DATABASE_URL=
